   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Waste Collector COVID-19 Support Fund</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Waste collectors are critical in a circular economy, yet are among the most marginalized people. Many are women and children living at the fringes of society, unable to access health care and education. Yet they play a vital role in their communities by removing waste and keeping materials out of the environment. They aren&apos;t equipped to be on the frontlines of the COVID-19 pandemic. We ask for your help to support their immediate needs while advancing better future conditions.</narrative>
  </description>
